UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText='We got to meet a Great One! Too bad it was during his nap time, but we understand. We like naps, too! Maybe we learn naps from Great Ones like we learn about shrines and shinies!$b$bCan we come back and visit the Great One again when not sleeping?' WHERE entry=13956;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText='You help Kekek learn him a book? Then, Kekek hunt with Hemet Nesingwary!' WHERE entry=13957;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText='Do we have to go back? We want to stay with you.' WHERE entry=13959;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText='It sounds like little Roo had a great time this week. I know he was getting awfully lonely in the orphanage and was eager to make some new friends. Thank you so much for agreeing to look after him.' WHERE entry=13959;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText='Kekek not want to go. Kekek want to see more of Northrend with Jeursey.' WHERE entry=13960;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText='Thank you for agreeing to care for Kekek this week. I know he can be a handful, but I think that with more individual attention and a few more friends, he\'ll do a lot better. No doubt he\'s going to be telling stories of his adventures with you for weeks.' WHERE entry=13960;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText='Oh! Hello there. I don\'t think we\'ve met; is there something I can do for you?' WHERE entry=13986;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText='Oh, my shield! I won\'t be using it anytime soon, but thank you. I hate that I\'m sitting here useless when I could be helping on the front, but fighting with my arm like this won\'t help anyone.$b$bTake care out there, won\'t you?' WHERE entry=13986;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText='<Crusader Rhydalla frowns.>$b$bDo you think they\'ve been planning this? I suppose it doesn\'t matter, but I don\'t like the implication that we\'ve been playing into their hands. Whatever is going on, we have to stop it.' WHERE entry=14016;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText='Did you find out what they\'re doing with the Black Knight\'s remains?' WHERE entry=14017;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText='The doctor will not have time to complete his work, but his plan is already in motion. From what you\'ve reported, the Lich King\s servants have reanimated and empowered the Black Knight and there\'s no telling what the knight\'s master has in mind. You have done well in uncovering this plot. I will tell High Crusader Adelard of your findings and together, we will alert the tournament\'s participants.' WHERE entry=14017;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText='Were you able to recover any of the missing supplies?' WHERE entry=14074;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText='These look a little worse for wear, but they\'re still edible. The crusaders will be glad to hear that we\'ve managed to recover some of the ship\'s cargo.' WHERE entry=14074;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText='Were you able to get those eggs? Those worms will start eating their handlers if they\'re not fed soon.' WHERE entry=14076;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText='Well done, $n. I\'ll take these to the Argent Crusade\'s keepers right away. They\'ll have no choice but to acknowledge that we\'re doing far more than the Sunreavers to keep the coliseum running smoothly.' WHERE entry=14076;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText='Have you seen to the spirits of the slain Tualiq villagers?' WHERE entry=14077;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText='<Narasi accepts the prayer book from you.>$b$bThank you. The book was a gift from Confessor Paletress herself. She would be honored to know that you have used it to bring tranquility to the slain.' WHERE entry=14077;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText='Have you shown the Kvaldir that we will not let them threaten us?' WHERE entry=14080;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText='Your actions have shown that we stand as one with the Argent Crusade, while the Sunreavers are too busy preening to take up their blades.' WHERE entry=14080;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText='Ah, you received my letter? Good.' WHERE entry IN (14082,14083,14081,14079,14084,14085,14086,14087,14088,14089);
