UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText='Have you managed to round up those snobolds yet? Gormok\'s anger shows no signs of lessening.' WHERE entry=14090;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText='The sooner we get these stinking things out of my sight and into their cage, the faster my mood will improve. I wish the Argent Crusade had given the Sunreavers the care of this creature. They\'re enough alike that they ought to be able to understand each other.' WHERE entry=14090;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText='Were you able to get those eggs? The jormungar are going to get nasty if they don\'t get fed.' WHERE entry=14092;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText='I\'ll let the crusaders know that you\'ve just returned with a fresh load of food while the Silver Covenant was sitting on its heels.' WHERE entry=14092;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText='I knew that Kraken was not a match for the likes of you.  Without that Kraken disrupting those boats, those Kvaldir will have no choice but to retreat.  Great job, Champion!' WHERE entry=14095;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText='Did you free Kul and those hopeless aspirants?' WHERE entry=14096;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText='Thanks to you, Kul and the aspirants will live fight the Scourge again. That\'s far from the first time someone\'s had to save Kul from himself. My only hope is that the crusaders can find a better outlet for his enthusiasm than allowing him to impart all of his bad habits to impressionable young aspirants.' WHERE entry=14096;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText='Hmmm, what brings you to seek the aid of the Earthen Ring?' WHERE entry=14100;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText='Ah, you\'ve mastered the four totems. You should be proud of your accomplishments so far, young $r, but this is only the beginning of your journey.$b$bHere, accept this gift from the Earthen Ring. Carry this relic with you and you will have the power of all four elements at your command.$b$bContinue your training, friend. Grave challenges are ahead for this world - I can hear it in the wind and feel it in the rumblings of the earth. We must be prepared for the worst.' WHERE entry=14100;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText='The defeat of the drottinn will set the kvaldir to fighting amongst themselves, buying us time to use our advantage. The crusade and the tournament are in your debt, champion.' WHERE entry=14101;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText='You have bought us valuable time to move against the Kvaldir and free the seas of these pests. Once again, the Argent Crusade is in your debt.' WHERE entry=14102;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText='Ornolf\'s crew will want to avenge their leader, but without him, they will be easier to defeat. We must live to carry out our mission, to see Icecrown rid of the Scourge and other evils.' WHERE entry=14104;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText='You are truly an example to all who have gathered beneath our banner, $n. Together, we will show the Scourge that we will not be defeated.' WHERE entry=14105;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText='Have you brought peace to the spirits of the fallen heroes?' WHERE entry=14107;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText='You have done our fallen brethren a great service and spared us the need to face them again on the field of battle. As our campaign against the Scourge progresses, I find myself thinking about my own fate.$b$bShould I fall, $n, I would want someone like you to do for me what you have done for the spirits of the fallen this day. I could not bear the thought of forcing my own brothers to slay me again and again.' WHERE entry=14107;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText='Have you driven away the Kraken yet? Hurry, Crusader! There isn\'t much time.' WHERE entry=14108;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText='Crusader, you may have bought those sailors just enough time to escape, Maybe next time, those Silver Covenant and Sunreavers will listen before running head first at the enemy.' WHERE entry=14108;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText='The spirits stir within you. What brings you to seek the aid of the Earthen Ring?' WHERE entry=14111;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText='I see you\'ve mastered use of the four totems. You are on your way to becoming one with the elemental spirits, but this is only the beginning of your journey.$b$bHere, accept this gift from the Earthen Ring. Carry this relic with you and you will have the power of all four elements at your command.$b$bYour training must continue! I sense a great many trials lie ahead for this world, and we will need the power of the elements behind us if we are to prevail.' WHERE entry=14111;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText='I hope you have something to feed Icehowl, otherwise I really will start bringing Sunreavers down to his cage.' WHERE entry=14112;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText='I\'m glad we\'ve gotten that done. It\'s not the most glorious task in the world, but when we partnered with the Argent Crusade, we promised to do all they asked of us without complaint. Of course, the same cannot be said of the Sunreavers.' WHERE entry=14112;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText='Great job, Champion. The fight continues, but now the Kvaldir know that we do not tolerate such attacks.' WHERE entry=14136;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText='Your actions have shown that we Sunreavers are far better allies to the Argent Crusade than the Silver Covenant and it is we who will be triumphant.' WHERE entry=14140;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText='Have you managed to round up those snobolds yet? Gormok\'s anger shows no signs of lessening.' WHERE entry=14141;
