UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText='Kul will live to embarrass himself again. That\'s far from the first time someone\'s had to save Kul from himself. With examples like him, it\'s no wonder most of the aspirants are taking up the habits of the Silver Covenant.' WHERE entry=14142;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText='Were you able to recover any of the missing supplies?' WHERE entry=14143;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText='These look a little worse for wear, but they\'re still edible. The crusaders will be glad to hear that we\'ve had some success. Maybe we can give the half-eaten ones to the Silver Covenant. That would make my day.' WHERE entry=14143;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText='Have you seen to the spirits of the slain Tualiq villagers?' WHERE entry=14144;
